    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. It runs and drives flawlessly with no mechanical issues. The exterior is free of damage, scratches, or blemishes. The interior is spotless with no wear to the seats, carpets, or trim. All systems and features function as intended.",
